Class DepsAwareTask.DepsSupplier<Impl>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.core.graph.transformation.executor.DepsAwareTask.DepsSupplier<Impl>
  • Type Parameters:
    Impl - the task type
    Enclosing class:
    DepsAwareTask<T,​Impl extends DepsAwareTask<T,​Impl>>
    public static class DepsAwareTask.DepsSupplier<Impl>
extends Object
    The dependency information of a task.

    The prereqSupplier is a supplier that returns a set of tasks necessary to compute depsSupplier. The depsSupplier is a supplier that returns the dependencies.
